00:33:50.400 --> 00:33:54.280
But when you talk about
Nigerian literature in English,

00:33:54.280 --> 00:33:57.890
there is a shortage of material
from the north of Nigeria.

00:33:57.890 --> 00:34:03.020
So I felt it was important to
kind of drag the north of Nigeria

00:34:03.020 --> 00:34:07.170
into the mainstream of Nigerian
literature in that sense and,

00:34:07.170 --> 00:34:09.870
