conversations about people.

00:34:09.870 --> 00:34:14.600
Because there's a lot of
misunderstanding, if you like,

00:34:14.600 --> 00:34:16.950
of why the different
people of Nigeria, you know,

00:34:16.950 --> 00:34:19.000
people in the east have
different ideas about the people

00:34:19.000 --> 00:34:20.360
