00:34:20.360 --> 00:34:21.660
So it's all over the place.

00:34:21.660 --> 00:34:26.260
And I felt that literature is one
of the ways that we could break

00:34:26.260 --> 00:34:29.370
down these barriers and create
that understanding of people.

00:34:29.370 --> 00:34:33.510
But because the north is not
writing its own stories in a way

00:34:33.510 --> 00:34:37.140
