00:37:41.900 --> 00:37:46.930
And the truth is that the
north is very conservative.

00:37:46.930 --> 00:37:51.270
It is a very religious
community in the sense

00:37:51.270 --> 00:37:53.840
that it is religious both ways.

00:37:53.840 --> 00:37:55.850
You know, the Muslim
north very religious;

00:37:55.850 --> 00:37:58.040
