character in my novel is a Muslim,

00:56:49.220 --> 00:56:52.560
is a northerner; but then
she has universal concerns

00:56:52.560 --> 00:56:57.980
that an average American has, that
an average Japanese person has.

00:56:57.980 --> 00:57:00.770
So these are the things that
